T02D3379:53a-1: ma h'a s'a ha sra pra marda ni s'a dha nam /
T02D3379:53a-3: stong chen mor rab tu 'joms ma zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3379:53a-4: 'phags ma stong chen mo rab tu 'joms ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3379:53a-5: sngon bzhin kho nar thams cad byas la /
T02D3379:53a-6: stong pa nyid kyi rjes su stong chen mo rab tu 'joms ma dkar mo zhal gcig ma /
T02D3379:53a-8: g-yas pa'i phyag gsum rnams su go rims ji lta bar ral gri dang /
T02D3379:53a-10: g-yon pa'i phyag gsum rnams su gzhu dang /
T02D3379:53a-12: sna tshogs pa'i cha lugs kyi na bza' dang /
T02D3379:53a-15: lang tshol babs pa'i gzugs sgeg pa la sogs pa'i
T02D3379:53a-16: yon tan can rnam par snang mdzad kyi dbu rgyan
T02D3379:53a-17: can / brum gyi sa bon las byung ba'i zla ba'i gdan dang zla ba'i rgyab rten can no //
T02D3379:53a-18: aom brum zhes pa'i sngags brjod par bya'o //
T02D3379:53b-0: @53b 'phags ma stong chen mo rab tu 'joms ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02D3379:53b-1: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
